Title: Adjusted
Description: The contents of the object have been adjusted.

Title: Not available
Description: The contents of the object are not available.

Title: Estimated
Description: The contents of the object are estimated. The code is typically used when measured values are missing and an estimate is made based on historical data.

Title: As provided
Description: The contents of the object are as provided.

Title: Incomplete
Description: The contents of the object are calculated based on incomplete data.

Title: Calculated
Description: The contents of the object are calculated. The code is typically used when a value is calculated based on several other known values.
